874
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:57,590
What happened? You lost something?

875
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:58,670
What did you lose?

876
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,240
Is this watch yours?

877
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,110
I lost it,

878
00:39:13,110 --> 00:39:14,840
but it wasn't originally mine.

879
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:39,150
When did Lang Bowen

880
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:40,410
lose this watch to you?

881
00:39:43,190 --> 00:39:44,120
About a year ago.

882
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:46,380
I don't remember clearly.

883
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:47,280
The information about this watch

884
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:48,360
is very important to us.

885
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:50,290
Think carefully before you speak.

886
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:54,070
I'll ask you this question again.

887
00:39:54,070 --> 00:39:55,280
The night of Ye Jian's incident,

888
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:56,740
did he come to Fenglinwan?

889
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,280
Mr. Lu.

890
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,280
Mr. Lu.

891
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:05,110
Let me remind you.

892
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,050
Without any evidence,

893
00:40:06,050 --> 00:40:06,630
we wouldn't be

894
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:08,290
coming to you again and again.

895
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:10,940
I gave you a chance.

896
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:14,240
This is really your last chance.

897
00:40:30,230 --> 00:40:30,810
Yes.

898
00:40:31,630 --> 00:40:32,340
He came.

899
00:40:33,150 --> 00:40:34,350
Why did Ye come to you?

900
00:40:36,190 --> 00:40:37,920
He also asked about that watch.

901
00:40:39,510 --> 00:40:41,310
Why didn't you tell us last time?

902
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:45,630
Later, Ye died.

903
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:48,980
I was afraid of getting into trouble.

904
00:41:01,210 --> 00:41:05,610
[The World's Jokes]

905
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:12,040
Mr. Rong.

906
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,230
Wait.

907
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:25,440
[The World's Jokes]

908
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:18,430
Let me ask you a question.

909
00:41:19,030 --> 00:41:20,510
A mushroom met an orange.

910
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:23,070
The mushroom told the orange to drop dead,

911
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:24,440
and the orange did.

912
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:25,190
Why?

913
00:41:27,550 --> 00:41:28,440
I don't know.

914
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:30,070
Do you know why recently

915
00:41:30,070 --> 00:41:30,630
I don't find jokes

916
00:41:30,630 --> 00:41:31,800
funny anymore?

917
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:35,550
Is Lu Yibo causing trouble

918
00:41:35,550 --> 00:41:36,270
again?

919
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,400
If he dares, I'll make him drop dead.

920
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:40,490
And you can take over Fenglinwan.

921
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:41,290
Mr. Rong,

922
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:42,590
I know something

923
00:41:42,590 --> 00:41:43,850
that will cheer you up.

924
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,030
Zhu Yifei

925
00:41:46,190 --> 00:41:47,610
will be in Sanjiangkou soon.

926
00:41:47,610 --> 00:41:49,340
We can make the deal right away.

927
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:51,680
Get to it then.

928
00:41:53,030 --> 00:41:53,920
Don't worry, Mr. Rong.

929
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,840
Zhu Yifei is

930
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,400
a big shot in the underworld.

931
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,800
He wouldn't do something as low as

932
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:58,680
selling fakes.

933
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:00,280
He's not a small fry.

934
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,340
[Zheng Yongbing]

935
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:11,340
I'll take this call first.

936
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:19,280
Hello?

937
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:20,000
Ren,

938
00:42:20,590 --> 00:42:21,440
can you sell the God of Wealth statue

939
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,240
back to me at the original price?

940
00:42:23,630 --> 00:42:24,560
Zheng Yongbing,

941
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,370
don't push your luck, okay?

942
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:27,840
Don't you know

943
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:28,630
how much I paid you

944
00:42:28,630 --> 00:42:29,890
for that piece of junk?

945
00:42:29,960 --> 00:42:30,670
Ren,

946
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:32,920
do you think I want to buy it back?

947
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:34,650
The investigators are onto me.

948
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,280
I have to return the stolen goods.

949
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,410
None of my business.

950
00:42:38,110 --> 00:42:39,070
Why would the investigators

951
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:40,730
care about your petty crimes?

952
00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:44,080
If I had known,

953
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:46,710
I would have melted it all down to sell,

954
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:47,550
instead of selling it to that woman

955
00:42:47,550 --> 00:42:48,410
at Fenglinwan.

956
00:42:50,110 --> 00:42:50,910
Wait a minute.

957
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:54,510
You're saying the police tracked you down

958
00:42:54,510 --> 00:42:55,710
through Fenglinwan?

959
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:56,720
That's right.

960
00:42:59,890 --> 00:43:00,970
Who's the woman?

961
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:01,960
Zhou Qi.

962
00:43:02,070 --> 00:43:03,470
I sold the jewelry to her,

963
00:43:03,550 --> 00:43:04,810
and she snitched on me.

964
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:05,480
Ren,

965
00:43:05,630 --> 00:43:07,360
I'll add another 20,000, okay?

966
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:09,610
Ren?
